      "title": "倫納德",
      "recipe": "bewitchment:nether_brick_leonard_statue",
      "recipe2": "bewitchment:scorned_brick_leonard_statue",
      "text": "倫納德是女巫的王。"
    },
    {
      "type": "crafting",
      "title": "巴弗滅",
